**PAGE 7 — SETTINGS: GENERAL**
Route: `/settings`

Reads: current user profile, org details, org plan.

Sections: Profile — name, email, change password. Organisation — name, industry, size, these are editable and write back to the organisations table. Preferences — default model per new project, timezone, email notification toggles.

Notification toggles control: analysis complete, API key health failure, weekly pool summary email, new team member joined. Each toggle writes to a user_preferences table immediately on change — no save button.

